# Deprecated — rules migrated to `.cursor/rules/`

All project conventions now live in `.cursor/rules/`:

| Rule file | Scope |
|-----------|-------|
| `00-language.mdc` | English-only artifacts |
| `01-quantum-ml-lab.mdc` | Experiment workflow, QML review |
| `02-architecture.mdc` | Layer boundaries (TypeScript backend) |
| `03-typescript-standards.mdc` | TS coding standards |
| `04-security.mdc` | Auth, multitenancy, RBAC |
| `05-testing.mdc` | TDD, test hierarchy |
| `06-observability.mdc` | Structured logging, health checks |
| `07-project-structure.mdc` | Canonical folder layout |

Do not edit this file — update the relevant `.mdc` rule instead.
